==Russian==
===Etymology===
Probably from [[не#Russian|не]] + [[ведать]], ‘not to know,’ indicating a strict hands-off relationship.

===Noun===
'''зять''' (zjat’) {{m}}

# [[son-in-law]]
# [[brother-in-law]] ''(the husband of one’s sister or sister-in-law)''

